{"tid":267082,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想獨佔一個朋友嘅諗法會唔會好變態？","createTime":"2017-06-02T03:55:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-02T09:00:36.000Z","uid":74824,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"93be26e01498a030a993eb034958357b27bc9864","tid":267082,"uid":74824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T03:55:02.000Z","msg":"一直同朋友A關係好好<br />\n就算得兩丁友都會一齊睇戲食飯打波<br />\n近排同一個本來唔太熟嘅朋友B熟絡咗<br />\n本來都冇乜野<br />\n但三個出去嘅時候發現佢地經常講一啲我唔知嘅野<br />\n原來係我唔知嘅情況下佢地變得成日單獨出去<br />\n仲好似成日刻意隱瞞唔想我知咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實會單獨出下街我覺得冇乜野<br />\n但當我感覺到佢地唔想比我知真係好唔好受<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到佢地一齊我覺得好討厭B<br />\n覺得佢搶咗我原來嘅位置<br />\n我咁諗會唔會好變態好病態<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"b2cadcb8e573736968720dcd9df5ae5b4f96b84f","tid":267082,"uid":271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T03:57:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">this</span>"},{"pid":"3805ba26b11927cd2c7eed1fecd6076e54d8d97a","tid":267082,"uid":3696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T04:00:59.000Z","msg":"偷偷地射啲精落佢樽水度 佢飲左就聽哂你話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d71c7640a1e1e5cb8f84d7e8c261c09f931e205","tid":267082,"uid":101490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T04:05:50.000Z","msg":"能成為蜜友大概總帶著愛<br />\n係愛呀哈利"},{"pid":"93ef39a8d261d5258a998d619e8c7be54d99a609","tid":267082,"uid":39316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T04:54:11.000Z","msg":"唔算變態<br />\n<br />\n但唔成熟<br />\n<br />\n人地要同邊個friend d係人地自由<br />\n你應該明白然後唔好再比呢種感覺困住自己"},{"pid":"c6a8bf5612ffacd12c5bfe4b1708ff4e59cdc3fc","tid":267082,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T04:58:19.000Z","msg":"gay"},{"pid":"b3268ec56f88824af4e2fb3eb292a5db7b240a91","tid":267082,"uid":74824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re